author: Suhas Nayse
title: Jr badminton meet: Gaurav, Sourabh qualify for main draw
text:
NAGPUR: Gaurav Mithe and Sourabh Kerhalkar have qualified for the main draw in the 24th Krishna Khaitan All India Junior Ranking Badminton tournament at Chandigarh on Wednesday.

While Gaurav, a student of Somalwar Nikalas School, made the cut in the U-17 boys singles, Sourabh advanced in the U-19 boys singles. Both the teenage city shuttlers did exceedingly well in the qualifying rounds.

The main draw matches will commence on Thursday. Stay updated on the go with Times of India News App. Click here to download it for your device.
